# Personal GMAIL account

IMAPAccount jorge
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User jorgeluisrojasb@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --decrypt --quiet ~/.dotfiles/passwords/.mbsyncpass-jorgeluisrojasb@gmail.com.gpg"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.3

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account jorge

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel jorge
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both 
Expunge Both
SyncState *


